                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8378" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1293</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1986 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奥马电器：冰箱出口大王的反并购战争</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Homa Appliances: The anti-merger war of the refrigerator export king</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘胜强，白浩然，童楠琦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东奥马电器有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奥马电器；TCL家电；反并购策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Homa Appliances; TCL Home Appliances; Anti-merger strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">反并购是指目标公司管理层为了防止公司控制权转移而采取的旨在预防或挫败并购者并购本公司的行为。中小企业在面临强势并购者时，往往难以找到合适的应对之法，而反并购则为其提供了更多决策的空间。本案例着重描述了TCL家电并购奥马电器过程中，面对TCL所发起的敌意并购，“冰箱出口大王”奥马电器巧用各类反并购策略，达到抬高并购成本、增加并购风险、阻碍并购的全过程。虽然奥马电器最终没能阻止TCL，被TCL家电收入囊中，但其对反并购策略的出色运用还是使得TCL付出了相当的代价。通过对本案例的学习，学员能够在全面学习反并购策略的同时，梳理出不同反并购策略的适用范围和作用影响，思考奥马电器反并购策略失败的原因。对于面临被并购或想要发起并购的企业，奥马电器对反并购策略的综合运用过程同样也具有重大参考意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Anti-merger refers to the actions taken by the management of the target company to prevent the transfer of the control of the company, aiming at preventing or discouraging the acquisition of the company. Small and medium-sized enterprises often find it difficult to find a suitable way to deal with the strong mergers and acquisitions, and anti-mergers provide them with more decision-making space. This case focuses on the process of TCL Home Appliances acquisition of Homa electrical equipment, in the face of the hostile merger initiated by TCL, &quot;refrigerator export king&quot; Homa Electrical equipment skillfully used various anti-merger strategies to increase the cost of merger, increase the risk of merger and acquisition, and hinder the whole process of merger and acquisition. Although Homa Electric finally failed to stop TCL, TCL Home Appliances in the pocket, but its excellent use of anti-merger strategy or TCL to pay a considerable price. Through the study of this case, the students can not only comprehensively learn the anti-merger strategy, but also sort out the scope of application and effect of different anti-merger strategies, and thinking about the reasons for the failure of the anti-merger strategy of Homa Electric. For enterprises that are facing mergers and acquisitions or want to initiate mergers and acquisitions, the comprehensive application process of the anti-merger strategy of Homa Electric is also of great reference significance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业反并购动因；企业并购动因；寻找“白衣骑士”；焦土战术；适时修改公司章程等反并购策略；委托代理理论；“隧道挖掘”问题</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
